Symbol.Script_3D:
! Retard Chamber
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- RETAIL CHAMBER --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
cx1 = SQR(RR^2 - (ConWidth_1/2)^2) cx2 = SQR(RR^2 - (ConWidth_2/2)^2)
GROUP "tank" ROTy -90 REVOLVE 5,360,1+2+16+32, 0,ConWidth_1/2, 1, cx1, 0, 901, cx1, RR, 3001, ZZYZX-cx2, RR, 1, ZZYZX, ConWidth_2/2, 1001 DEL 1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "Pipe" ROTy -90 ADDx ConPosZ_3 ROTx 180 ROTz 90
IF ConStatus_3 THEN CYLIND ConPosX_3, ConWidth_3/2 ENDIF DEl 4 ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP ADDGROUP("tank", "Pipe") KILLGROUP "tank" KILLGROUP "Pipe"
DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 1 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Retard Chamber DrawingNum = 1
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 0, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 1 DEL TOP
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- RETAIL CHAMBER --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, RR, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -RR, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 RR, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -RR, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN POLY2_B 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0, 901, RR,360,4001 CIRCLE2 0,0, ConWidth_2/2 ENDIF
ENDIF
END
